      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hearing you say you're so deeply exhausted in your bones tells me you are in a place of profound pain right now. When the weight of everything feels too heavy to carry, the thought of stopping can seem like the only relief available. Please know that there are people who want to help you carry this weight, and you don't have to go through this silence alone. Please reach out immediately to a crisis hotline or emergency services.",
      "source": "target",
